OL,3,CSite of Britain's only WW1 battlefield
OL,4,Cgiven #500,000 to secure future
OL,6,FKris Jepson has been to the site of
OL,7,FBritain's only WW1 battlefield. Watch
OL,8,Fthe full video on ITVX
OL,10,FThe Heugh Battery Museum has been
OL,11,Fawarded almost #500,000 for urgent
OL,12,Fworks on the Scheduled Monument part
OL,13,Fof the site.
OL,15,FThe money to repair the gun battery
OL,16,Fcomes from the Cultural Investment
OL,17,FFund and is to preserve the site of
OL,18,Fnational archaeological importance.
