OL,6,FOver the years, the saltwater of the
OL,7,Fcoast and the amount of visitors to
OL,8,Fthe battery has worsened the condition
OL,9,Fof the battery which was not built to
OL,10,Flast for over a century.
OL,12,F"It is a very old building," museum
OL,13,Fmanager Diane Stephens explained. "It
OL,14,Fwas built of concrete, it wasn't meant
OL,15,Fto last and it wasn't meant to be a
OL,16,Fmuseum with all of the tread and all
OL,17,Foff the people who come around it and
OL,18,Fuse it and touch it.
OL,20,F"The weather, the salt water doesn't
OL,21,Fhelp so it is just an ongoing battle.
