OL,6,F"If we can stabilise the monument side
OL,7,Fof things and hopefully if we can get
OL,8,Fa new building we can get a lot more
OL,9,Fof our collection on show it will make
OL,10,Fit a much better visitor attraction.
OL,12,F"We have great plans for this place so
OL,13,Fwatch this space and come and see us."
OL,15,FIt is hoped the money awarded will
OL,16,Fhelp stabilise the concrete structures
OL,17,Fof the monument, repair drainage
OL,18,Fsystems, improve ventilation and add
OL,19,Fextra safety features.
