OL,6,FDr Reeve continued: "The difference in
OL,7,Freporting rankled with people in
OL,8,FHartlepool because they were affected
OL,9,Freally badly, in this really exposed
OL,10,Fpart of the North East coast,
OL,11,FGermany's not too far away, they were
OL,12,Fhit first, yet they didn't get any
OL,13,Fattention.
OL,15,F"Being the plucky working class town
OL,16,Fthat it is, they kind of took it on
OL,17,Fthe chin. Then people tried to make
OL,18,Fsense of what happened and rebuild
OL,19,Ffrom it."
