OL,6,FA magazine is situated underneath the
OL,7,Fbattery and would have housed around
OL,8,F500 shells which could be used.
OL,10,FOne person who would have been
OL,11,Ffamiliar with it is Robyn Foster's
OL,12,FGreat-Grandfather, Bombardier John
OL,13,FJames Hope. He is believed to have
OL,14,Ffired the most rounds of shells at the
OL,15,FGerman ships on the day and was one of
OL,16,Fthe first to be awarded a medal for
OL,17,Fbravery for his actions during the bomb
