OL,6,FMs Foster told ITV Tyne Tees: "We're
OL,7,Freally proud of the fact he's part of
OL,8,Four family and he's part of the
OL,9,FHartlepool history.
OL,11,F"It's brilliant that we're able to
OL,12,Fcome to the battery to see what
OL,13,Fhappened on the day and have the
OL,14,Fhistory of it. We've found out a lot
OL,15,Fof information about my great granda'
OL,16,Ffrom historians that are based here.
