OL,6,F"She (my grandmother) never wanted to
OL,7,Ftalk about it but occasionally it came
OL,8,Fout. She told me they climbed out
OL,9,Fbecause the staircase no longer
OL,10,Fexisted, and Uncle Billy developed a
OL,11,Fstammer which he had for the rest of
OL,12,Fhis life."
OL,14,FThe Heugh Battery Museum is central to
OL,15,Fhelping tell the stories of those on
OL,16,Fthe Hartlepool headland during the day
OL,17,Fof the bombardment. The funding
OL,18,Fprovided will help to ensure that will
OL,19,Fcontinue to be the case for years to
OL,20,Fcome.
